&lt;h3&gt;validation-mode&lt;/h3&gt;

The `validation-mode` XML element specifies the [`ValidationMode`](https://docs.oracle.com/javaee/7/api/javax/persistence/ValidationMode.html) strategy, which instructs the JPA provider whether it should check the entities Bean Validation at runtime.

